---
title: Pacific-Style Chicken Burger with Charred Pineapple & Wedges
description: A chicken burger this good is going to create waves of cheers without even trying. Ride out the praise on a current of flavour from Caribbean jerk seasoning to sweet and juicy pineapple. It’s a winning dinner with a side of wedges, perfect for dipping in some mayonnaise.
